    <para id="import-auto-id2578578">Finally, substituting the value for <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>I</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{I rSub { size 8{1} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> into the fifth equation gives</para>
